&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Per Diem:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;$200/day. Technician is responsible for lodging, transportation, meals, and incidental expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expense Reimbursement Option:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;$68/day per diem plus company-paid/reimbursed lodging, rental car, and approved travel expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
