&lt;li&gt;Verify proper bolt materials, lubricants, gasket selection, torque values, and installation methods prior to assembly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret engineering drawings, maintenance procedures, work packages, and technical specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform flange management activities to ensure proper joint integrity and system reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document completed work activities in accordance with nuclear quality assurance and maintenance requirements&lt;/li&gt;
